strings: <voice_0x0100156F><se_def>Rhapthorne: He has been a stubborn one, but with your help I can finally control this flesh as my own.
<voice_0x01001570><se_def>Rhapthorne: Now that this fool has disposed of the Lord High Priest for me, the final heir is no more and the seal of the sceptre is broken!
<voice_0x01001571><se_def>Rhapthorne: Yes! The time has come for my resurrection!

<voice_0x01001573><se_def>Rhapthorne: Complete my revival!
My revival to flesh and blood!
